folder: Grand Street & Wooster Street, Manhattan, NY
text:
69-59 Grand Street, south side, at, adjoining, and west of the S.W. corner of Wooster Street. June 23, 1933.

P. L. Sperr.

folder: Wooster Street & Grand Street, Manhattan, NY
text:
Wooster Street, south from Grand Street to its southern end at Canal Street. Wooster Street is the third of a group of seven streets laid out parallel to and west of Broadway. The building in the background is the new New York Telephone Building. June 23, 1933.

P. L. Sperr.
